gw.api.team

Class TeamModel

  • gw.api.team.TeamModel

  • public class TeamModel
    Basic interface common to all subclasses of TeamModel. Primary type to be passed around in application-specific PCF files. Sub-interface off of this to define appplication-specific flags and functionality, then subclass off the corresponding class and implement that interface on the application side.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      Group[] ChildGroupsSortedByName
      Gets all child groups of this model, sorted by name.
      GroupUser[] ChildUsersSortedByName
      Gets all child users of this model, sorted by name.
      boolean Folder
      Returns true if this TeamModel should appear as a folder in the TeamTree.
      Object Id
      Returns a unique identifier for the data, to be used in TeamTree caching.
      String Label
      Returns the display label for this element of data.
      TeamModel[] SubModels
      Returns all the TeamDatas that belong properly to this TeamModel, in the order they should appear in the TeamTree.
